A cinematic film shot of a young man and a wan_womodel_01 seating in the backseat of a vintage car with a tan leather interior. Man leans foreward towards the driver and looking at him. wan_womodel_01 seats on the left backseat. They are both wearing denim jackets. Natural skin tones. Detailed skin. The style is of a fashion campaign.
Medium close-up shot, camera framing back of the car from between the front seats, looking directly with back window in the middle of the background.  Shot is captured with a prime lens 20mm, wide aperture f/1.8.
Warn, cinematic color grading. Natural skin tones. A color palette dominated by rich denim blues, earthy browns, and warm tans from the car's interior. Pop of red shirt of the driver's shoulder in the right foreground.
Shallow depth of field, with the wan_womodel_01 in the mid-ground in sharp focus. The background seen through the car windows is softly blurred with bokeh. A foreground element creates layers and a sense of immersion within the car.

Bright, natural directional sunlight streams in from the side car window (camera left). This creates soft highlights on the subjects' faces and clothing. The lighting feels warm and cinematic, with a pleasant contrast between the bright exterior and the shaded car interior. 
Part of fashion campaign built around themes of freedom, youth, nostalgia, and authentic connection
